{"id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0001","text":"長街燈光太亮了 瞳孔收縮了","structure":{"line_index":1,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["環境的壓迫感","生理的不適"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["燈光","太亮","瞳孔","收縮"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,3,3,3,4,2,5,0,9,3,3,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["coeng4","gaai1","dang1","gwong1","taai3","loeng6","liu5","tung4","hung2","sau1","suk1","liu5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"長街","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"燈光","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"太亮","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"了","pos":"PART"},{"text":"瞳孔","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"收縮","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"了","pos":"PART"}],"syntax_notes":"以環境的強烈刺激（燈光太亮）引發生理反應（瞳孔收縮），營造一種不適感。"},"source":{"title":"臨睡吻你一次","artists":["郭富城"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2800","prev_line_id":null,"next_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0002","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0002","text":"而我像沒能力對焦","structure":{"line_index":2,"char_count":8},"semantics":{"themes":["無力感","失焦"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["沒能力","對焦"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,5,2,2,0,2,4,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ji4","ngo5","zoeng6","mut6","nang4","lik6","deoi3","ziu1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"而","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"像","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"沒","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"能力","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"對焦","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"以「像」字連接，比喻自己處於一種失焦、無力的狀態，呼應上一行的生理不適。"},"source":{"title":"臨睡吻你一次","artists":["郭富城"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2800","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0001","next_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0003","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0003","text":"撐不了我仍苦笑 多一秒也求一秒","structure":{"line_index":3,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["掙扎","渴望","痛苦"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["撐不了","苦笑","求"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,5,5,0,9,4,3,3,5,5,0,3,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["caang1","bat1","liu5","ngo5","jing4","fu2","siu3","do1","jat1","miu5","jaa5","kau4","jat1","miu5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"撐","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不了","pos":"PART"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"仍","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"苦笑","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"多一秒","pos":"NUM"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"求","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"一秒","pos":"NUM"}],"syntax_notes":"「撐不了」與「苦笑」形成對比，表達即使處於困境仍強顏歡笑的無奈，並極力渴望多一點時間。"},"source":{"title":"臨睡吻你一次","artists":["郭富城"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2800","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0002","next_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0004","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0004","text":"因心中找到呼吸必要","structure":{"line_index":4,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["生存的意志","愛情的支撐"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["心中","呼吸","必要"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,3,9,4,3,3,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jan1","sam1","zung1","zaau2","dou3","fu1","kap1","bit1","jiu3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"因","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"心中","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"找到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"呼吸","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"必要","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"「因」字連接，解釋上一行苦笑的原因，即心中仍有愛情的支撐，是活下去的動力。"},"source":{"title":"臨睡吻你一次","artists":["郭富城"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2800","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0003","next_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0005","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0005","text":"如身體充滿亂箭 如生死一線","structure":{"line_index":5,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["危機","生命的脆弱"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["亂箭","生死一線"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,3,9,3,5,2,4,0,3,9,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jyu4","san1","tai2","cung1","mun5","lyun6","zin3","jyu4","sang1","sei2","jat1","sin3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"如","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"身體","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"充滿","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"亂箭","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"如","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"生死","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"一線","pos":"NUM"}],"syntax_notes":"使用「如」字開頭的比喻，描繪身體狀況極差，生命危在旦夕的危險處境。"},"source":{"title":"臨睡吻你一次","artists":["郭富城"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2800","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0004","next_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0006","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0006","text":"而你面目浮現半天","structure":{"line_index":6,"char_count":8},"semantics":{"themes":["希望","慰藉"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["面目","浮現"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,5,2,2,0,2,4,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ji4","nei5","min6","muk6","fau4","jin6","bun3","tin1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"而","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"面目","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"浮現","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"半天","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「而」字轉折，在極度危險的時刻，愛人的形象出現，帶來一絲希望與慰藉。"},"source":{"title":"臨睡吻你一次","artists":["郭富城"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2800","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0005","next_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0007","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0007","text":"當空氣已全污染 當失意再無底線","structure":{"line_index":7,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["絕望","困境"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["空氣污染","失意","底線"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,4,5,0,3,5,3,4,4,0,9,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["hung1","hei3","ji5","cyun4","wu1","jim5","sat1","ji3","zoi3","mou4","dai2","sin3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"當","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"空氣","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"已全","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"污染","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"當","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"失意","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"再","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"無","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"底線","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「當」字開頭的兩個分句，描繪了極度惡劣的外部環境和內心絕望的狀態，達到無可挽回的境地。"},"source":{"title":"臨睡吻你一次","artists":["郭富城"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2800","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0006","next_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0008","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0008","text":"你也是無悔在身邊","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":8},"semantics":{"themes":["陪伴","支持"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["無悔","身邊"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,5,2,0,4,2,3,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["nei5","jaa5","si6","mou4","fui3","zoi6","san1","bin1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"無悔","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"在","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"身邊","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「也」字強調，即使在如此惡劣的環境下，對方依然無悔地陪伴在身邊，給予力量。"},"source":{"title":"臨睡吻你一次","artists":["郭富城"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2800","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0007","next_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0009","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0009","text":"從今開始 臨睡吻你一次","structure":{"line_index":9,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["承諾","珍惜","愛"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["從今開始","臨睡","吻"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,3,3,9,0,2,5,5,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["cung4","gam1","hoi1","ci2","lam4","seoi6","man5","nei5","jat1","ci3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"從今開始","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"臨睡","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"吻","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"一次","pos":"NUM"}],"syntax_notes":"「從今開始」標誌著一個新的決定，表達了對愛人深深的珍惜和愛意，要在睡前給予親吻。"},"source":{"title":"臨睡吻你一次","artists":["郭富城"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2800","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0008","next_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0010","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0010","text":"我想保證 如時光終止","structure":{"line_index":10,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["承諾","永恆"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["保證","時光終止"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,9,9,4,0,0,3,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","soeng2","bou2","zing3","jyu4","si4","gwong1","zung1","zi2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"想","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"保證","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"如","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"時光","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"終止","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「我想保證」表達了堅定的意願，即使面對時間的終結，也要珍惜當下。"},"source":{"title":"臨睡吻你一次","artists":["郭富城"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2800","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0009","next_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0011","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0011","text":"在這生得到的最後體溫","structure":{"line_index":11,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["珍貴","愛情的溫度"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["得到","最後","體溫"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,3,3,4,3,4,2,9,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zoi6","ze5","sang1","dak1","dou3","dik1","zeoi3","hau6","tai2","wan1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"在","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"這生","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"得到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"最後","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"體溫","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"強調在生命最後的時刻，所能得到的「體溫」是多麼珍貴，是愛情的體現。"},"source":{"title":"臨睡吻你一次","artists":["郭富城"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2800","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0010","next_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0012","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
