{"id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0013","text":"從今開始 臨睡抱你一次","structure":{"line_index":13,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["承諾","珍惜","愛"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["從今開始","臨睡","抱"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,3,3,9,0,2,5,5,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["cung4","gam1","hoi1","ci2","lam4","seoi6","pou5","nei5","jat1","ci3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"從今開始","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"臨睡","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"抱","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"一次","pos":"NUM"}],"syntax_notes":"重複「從今開始」，並將「吻」換成「抱」，進一步表達對愛人的珍惜和親密接觸的渴望。"},"source":{"title":"臨睡吻你一次","artists":["郭富城"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2800","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0012","next_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0014","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0014","text":"不可保證 世間那刻終止","structure":{"line_index":14,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["不確定","珍惜當下"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["不可保證","世間","終止"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,9,9,4,4,5,3,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["bat1","ho2","bou2","zing3","sai3","naa5","hak1","zung1","zi2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"不可","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"保證","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"世間","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"那刻","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"終止","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「不可保證」與上一段的「我想保證」形成對比，承認現實的不確定性，但仍強調珍惜當下。"},"source":{"title":"臨睡吻你一次","artists":["郭富城"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2800","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0013","next_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0015","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0015","text":"尚有體力時 尚能感動時","structure":{"line_index":15,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["堅持","愛","付出"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["體力","感動","時"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,9,2,0,2,0,9,2,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["soeng6","jau5","tai2","lik6","si4","soeng6","nang4","gam2","dung6","si4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"尚有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"體力","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"時","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"尚","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"能","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"感動","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"時","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「尚有...時」的條件句，表達只要還有體力和感動的能力，就會繼續付出愛。"},"source":{"title":"臨睡吻你一次","artists":["郭富城"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2800","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0014","next_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0016","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0016","text":"多睏倦仍樂意","structure":{"line_index":16,"char_count":6},"semantics":{"themes":["愛","付出","溫柔"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["睏倦","樂意"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,4,2,0,2,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["do1","kwan3","gyun6","jing4","lok6","ji3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"多","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"睏倦","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"仍","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"樂意","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「多睏倦仍樂意」表達了即使疲憊，也甘願為愛付出，充滿溫柔的語氣。"},"source":{"title":"臨睡吻你一次","artists":["郭富城"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2800","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0015","next_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0017","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0017","text":"用每一呼氣輕吹 你雙耳","structure":{"line_index":17,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["親密","愛撫","溫柔"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["呼氣","輕吹","雙耳"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,3,3,4,3,3,5,3,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jung6","mui5","jat1","fu1","hei3","hing1","ceoi1","nei5","soeng1","ji5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"用","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"每","pos":"DET"},{"text":"一","pos":"NUM"},{"text":"呼氣","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"輕吹","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"雙耳","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"描繪了親暱的動作「輕吹雙耳」，充滿愛意和溫柔的細膩情感。"},"source":{"title":"臨睡吻你一次","artists":["郭富城"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2800","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0016","next_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0018","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0018","text":"颱風都吹過萬次 危急多少次","structure":{"line_index":18,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["考驗","艱難","共同經歷"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["颱風","危急","萬次"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,3,3,3,4,2,4,0,3,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["toi4","fung1","dou1","ceoi1","gwo3","maan6","ci3","ngai4","gap1","do1","ci3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"颱風","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"都","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"吹","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"過","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"萬次","pos":"NUM"},{"text":"危急","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"多少","pos":"NUM"},{"text":"次","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"以極端的自然災害（颱風）和危機情況（危急）來比喻人生中經歷的種種艱難困苦。"},"source":{"title":"臨睡吻你一次","artists":["郭富城"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2800","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0017","next_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0019","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0019","text":"和你共渡纏住尾指","structure":{"line_index":19,"char_count":8},"semantics":{"themes":["陪伴","扶持","愛情"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["共渡","纏住","尾指"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,5,2,2,0,2,5,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["wo4","nei5","gung6","dou6","cin4","zyu6","mei5","zi2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"和","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"共渡","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"纏住","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"尾指","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「共渡」和「纏住尾指」描繪了兩人共同經歷風雨，互相扶持的畫面，象徵著堅定的愛情。"},"source":{"title":"臨睡吻你一次","artists":["郭富城"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2800","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0018","next_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0020","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0020","text":"當舉世再無都市 當都市再無景緻","structure":{"line_index":20,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["末世","孤獨","絕望"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["舉世","無都市","無景緻"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[9,4,4,0,3,5,3,5,4,0,9,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["geoi2","sai3","zoi3","mou4","dou1","si5","dou1","si5","zoi3","mou4","ging2","zi3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"當","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"舉世","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"再","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"無","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"都市","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"當","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"都市","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"再","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"無","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"景緻","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「當」字開頭的兩個分句，描繪了極致的末世景象，世界毀滅，失去一切，營造極度絕望的氛圍。"},"source":{"title":"臨睡吻你一次","artists":["郭富城"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2800","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0019","next_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0021","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0021","text":"你也是和我在相依","structure":{"line_index":21,"char_count":8},"semantics":{"themes":["依偎","愛","陪伴"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["相依"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,5,2,0,5,2,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["nei5","jaa5","si6","wo4","ngo5","zoi6","ji1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"和","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"在","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"相依","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「也」字強調，即使在世界毀滅的末日，兩人依然互相依偎，愛意永恆。"},"source":{"title":"臨睡吻你一次","artists":["郭富城"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2800","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YOt5a-M5Z-O_MjgwMA_0020","next_line_id":null,"paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
